31
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:44,477
Where do you live?

32
00:03:45,600 --> 00:03:47,795
Park Avenue, just below the train station.

33
00:03:48,760 --> 00:03:50,193
Climb aboard.

34
00:04:03,040 --> 00:04:05,873
