134
00:11:08,520 --> 00:11:12,195
Boundless energy,
euphoria alternating with exhaustion.

135
00:11:12,280 --> 00:11:17,195
Insomnia, paranoia,
a compulsion to itch, hallucinations.

136
00:11:18,920 --> 00:11:21,514
In nursing school,
I treated some soldiers who were addicted.

137
00:11:21,600 --> 00:11:23,033
